---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Commercial Carpet Cleaning"
  description="Commercial carpet cleaning service for offices and businesses. Competitive rates, flexible schedules, and superior results. Free estimate."
>
  <!-- SPLIT SCREEN HERO -->
  <div class="split-hero-container">
    <div class="container full-width-split">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <!-- LEFT COLUMN: CONTENT (Hook) -->
        <div class="split-content fade-in-section">
          <span class="service-cat-badge">COMMERCIAL</span>
          <h1 class="split-title fade-in-up text-gradient-empire">
            Commercial Carpet Cleaning
          </h1>

          <div class="problem-statement fade-in-up delay-100">
            <h3 class="problem-title">The Problem:</h3>
            <p class="problem-text">
              Your company's image starts with cleanliness. Stained or dusty
              carpets harm your reputation and the air quality of your offices.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="lead-text fade-in-up delay-200">
            A professional maintenance service designed for your business
            spaces. Flexible plans, quick drying, and impeccable results for
            offices and retail.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-group fade-in-up delay-300">
            <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-primary pulse-btn">
              <span class="icon">📞</span> (514) 893-9939 (Free Estimate)
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary-outline">
              <span class="icon">✉️</span> Online Quote
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: IMAGE (Visual / Slideshow) -->
        <div class="split-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-200">
          <div class="slideshow-container">
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-14.webp"
              alt="Commercial carpet cleaning"
              class="slide active"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-18.webp"
              alt="Clean office"
              class="slide"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-19.webp"
              alt="Professional maintenance"
              class="slide"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-30.webp"
              alt="Quick drying"
              class="slide"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-31.webp"
              alt="Impeccable result"
              class="slide"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout">
        <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
        <div class="service-main">
          <!-- BENEFIT LIST & SEO CONTENT -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-100">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Solutions for Offices and Businesses
            </h2>

            <p>Maximize the lifespan of your investments:</p>

            <ul class="benefit-list">
              <li>
                <strong>Building entrances and corridors:</strong> High-performance
                cleaning for high-traffic areas.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Reception halls and offices:</strong> Careful maintenance
                for carpets, chairs, and cubicles.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Building hallways and stairs:</strong> Complete solutions
                for all your common areas.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
              <button id="toggle-seo-btn" class="btn-text-reveal">
                Learn more about commercial carpet cleaning ▼
              </button>
            </div>

            <div id="seo-content" class="seo-content-hidden">
              <hr class="separator" />
              <h3>Commercial Expertise and Large Spaces</h3>
              <p>
                At <strong>Empire Cleaning Group</strong>, we understand that
                the cleanliness of your professional premises—from <strong
                  >building entrances</strong
                > to <strong>reception halls</strong>—reflects your company’s
                image. We offer a specialized service for all types of flooring
                (commercial carpet, tiles) in <strong
                  >offices, retail, and common areas</strong
                > in Montreal.
              </p>
              <p>
                Our professional equipment (Truck-mount or Portable) allows us
                to effectively treat <strong>building hallways</strong>, <strong
                  >staircases</strong
                >, and large open spaces. We eliminate salt, calcium, and
                embedded dirt to restore your carpets to their original shine.
              </p>

              <h3>Our adapted solutions:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Common area maintenance:</strong> Impeccable hallways, corridors,
                  and entrance halls.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Complete cleaning:</strong> Carpets, chairs, cubicles, and
                  waiting room sofas.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Quick drying:</strong> Ecological products and powerful
                  suction for rapid reuse of the premises.
                </li>
              </ul>

              <p>
                Whether for a one-time <strong
                  >commercial carpet cleaning</strong
                > or recurring maintenance of your <strong
                  >building entrances</strong
                >, our team guarantees a professional result. Contact us for a
                free estimate per square foot.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  // Simple Cross-Fade Slideshow
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");

  if (slides.length > 0) {
    let currentSlide = 0;
    const intervalTime = 4000; // 4 seconds

    setInterval(() => {
      slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
      currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
      slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
    }, intervalTime);
  }

  // Toggle SEO Content
  const toggleBtn = document.getElementById("toggle-seo-btn");
  const seoContent = document.getElementById("seo-content");

  if (toggleBtn && seoContent) {
    toggleBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
      seoContent.classList.toggle("visible");
      if (seoContent.classList.contains("visible")) {
        toggleBtn.textContent = "Show less ▲";
      } else {
        toggleBtn.textContent = "Learn more about commercial carpet cleaning ▼";
      }
    });
  }
</script>

<style>
  /* HERO */
  /* SPLIT SCREEN HERO (Sky Blue Theme) */
  .split-hero-container {
    background-color: #fff; /* Reset container to white */
    padding-top: 0; /* Remove container padding so image hits top */
    padding-bottom: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 100vw;
  }

  .full-width-split {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .split-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: stretch;
    min-height: 80vh; /* Consistent viewport height */
  }

  /* LEFT TEXT COLUMN */
  .split-content {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 100px 4rem 4rem 10%; /* Add header offset internal padding */
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .service-cat-badge {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .split-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 3.5vw, 4rem);
    color: var(--color-primary); /* Dark Blue text */
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .problem-statement {
    background: #ffffff; /* White box */
    border-left: 4px solid #ff4444; /* Red border returns for alertness */
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 206, 235, 0.3); /* Soft blue shadow */
  }

  .problem-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #cc0000;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .problem-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .lead-text {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-main); /* Dark grey text */
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 650px;
  }

  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Reset Secondary Button for Light Mode */
  .split-content .btn-secondary-outline {
    border-color: #ddd;
    color: #666;
  }
  .split-content .btn-secondary-outline:hover {
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  /* RIGHT IMAGE COLUMN */
  .split-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 500px;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 0;
    transform: none;
    box-shadow: none;
    margin: 0;
    background-color: #fff; /* Ensure white background if image loads late */
  }

  /* Slideshow Styles reused but adapted for full height */
  .slideshow-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .slide {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }

  .slide.active {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .split-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .split-content {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
      order: 1; /* Content first */
    }

    .split-image-wrapper {
      order: 2; /* Image second */
      height: 400px;
      min-height: 0;
    }

    .lead-text {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  /* LAYOUT */
  .service-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Full width for content now since we have a different layout */
    gap: 5rem;
  }

  /* TYPOGRAPHY */
  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  /* SEO Content & Toggle Styles */
  .btn-text-reveal {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-text-reveal:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .seo-content-hidden {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
  }

  .seo-content-hidden.visible {
    display: block;
  }

  .separator {
    border: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  /* Additional text styling for SEO section */
  .seo-content-hidden p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
  }

  .seo-content-hidden strong {
    color: var(--color-empire-red);
  }

  .seo-content-hidden ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .seo-content-hidden li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Benefit List Styles from original */
  .benefit-list {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    list-style: none; /* Ensure no default bullets */
    padding: 0;
  }

  .benefit-list li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .benefit-list li::before {
    content: "✓";
    color: #d32f2f; /* Empire Red or Gold */
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
